elements.contents: ... that the flat wooden ceiling of St. Martin (pictured), the Lutheran main church of Sindelfingen built in the 11th century, is still preserved?

elements.title: Cephas L. Bard
elements.contents: ... that Cephas L. Bard, the first American physician in Ventura, California, was also the first person to die in the hospital he built there?

elements.title: Eurovision Song Contest 1957

elements.title: Geliyoo
